text: Girls5eva is an American musical comedy television series created by Meredith Scardino. It premiered on May 6, 2021, on Disney Channel. The series centers on four women who were part of a girl group named Girls5eva in te 1990s. The girl group was popular around the 2000 before fading into one-hit-wonder status. Now unfulfilled in their various lives, the women reunite in an attempt to find musical success again. One of Girls5eva's hit songs is sampled by a rapper named Lil Stinker. ==References== Category:2021 American television series debuts Category:2020s American comedy television series
